                                <p>Our products are digital and delivered instantly:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Instant Access:</strong> You receive product access immediately after successful payment</li>
                                    <li><strong>Access Period:</strong> Access duration varies by product (check product description)</li>
